title: SUPERMODEL 10 MINUTE INTERVAL RUN | Treadmill Follow Along with IBX Running
description:
Today we are crushing this quick 10 minute treadmill interval run by Danish supermodel Nina Agdal! She is super passionate about the fitness space and we love this walk-run hill interval workout! Coach Rachael will take you through it

12:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com

01:40 - Workout!
11:40 - Cool Down
